# ------------------ Gmail -----------------------------------

IMAPAccount gmail
Host imap.gmail.com
User ah74230@gmail.com
PassCmd "cat ~/.secrets/.oh-no-insecure-password"
SSLType IMAPS
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

IMAPStore gmail-remote
Account gmail

MaildirStore gmail-local
Subfolders Verbatim
Path ~/documents/mail/Gmail/
Inbox ~/documents/mail/Gmail/INBOX
# Trash [Gmail]/Bin/

# With mbsync 1.4.0 and later: Use 'Far' instead of 'Master', and
# 'Near' instead of 'Slave'.
Channel gmail
Far :gmail-remote:
Near :gmail-local:
Patterns  ![Gmail]* "INBOX" "[Gmail]/Sent Mail" "[Gmail]/Starred" "[Gmail]/All Mail" "[Gmail]/Bin"
Expunge Both
Create Both
SyncState *

